article.description: — Shelby Adams registered 15 points as Texas State defeated Incarnate Word 72-64 on Saturday.
article.headline: Adams carries Texas State over Incarnate Word 72-64
article.linkText: Adams carries Texas State over Incarnate Word 72-64
article.story: SAN MARCOS, Texas -- — Shelby Adams registered 15 points as Texas State defeated Incarnate Word 72-64 on Saturday. Marlin Davis had 12 points and seven assists for Texas State (3-1). Nighael Ceaser and Mason Harrell added 10 points apiece. Keaston Willis had 16 points and six rebounds for the Cardinals (1-3). Marcus Larsson added 14 points and 10 rebounds. Des Balentine had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
